<style>

  #imageOne {
    background-image: url('{{ section.settings.image1 | img_url: '1200x1200' }}');
  }
  #imageTwo {
    background-image: url('{{ section.settings.image2 | img_url: '1200x1200' }}');
  }
  #imageThree {
    background-image: url('{{ section.settings.image3 | img_url: '1200x1200' }}');
  }

  .img-container {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }
  .image-class {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-size: 100% 100%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center center;
  }
  #imageTwo {
    display: none;
  }
  #imageThree {
    display: none;
  }
  #Accordion-Container {
    width: 50%;
    flex: 1.5;
  }
  .accordion-Section {
    min-width: 380px;
    background-color: #2B2A2A;
    min-height: 418px;
    display: flex;
  }
  .accordion-item {
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid white;
    border-radius: none;
  }
  button.accordion-button {
    font-size: 30px;
    font-family: 'Roboto';
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .accordion-button:focus {
    border-color: none !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
  }

  .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) {
    color: white;
    background-color: #2B2A2A !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
  }
  button.accordion-button.collapsed {
    background: #2B2A2A;
    color: white;
  }
  .accordion-body {
    background: #2B2A2A;
    color: white;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    padding-bottom: 33px;
    line-height: 31px;
  }
  .accordion-button:after {
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml, <svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 16 16' fill='%23ffffff'><path fill-rule='evenodd' d='M1.646 4.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0L8 10.293l5.646-5.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708.708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-6-6a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708z'/></svg>") !important;
  }
  a.accordion-btn {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
    border: 1px solid white;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    display: block;
    font-size: 20px;
    width: 126px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-radius: 30px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  {% comment %}
    .image-class {
      width: 728px;
      height: 420px;
    }
  {% endcomment %}
  .accordion-img {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    /* min-width: 50%; */
    width: 100%;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .img-container {
    max-width: 655px;
    min-width:380px ;
  }
  .accordion-item:last-of-type {
    border-radius: 0;
  }
  .accordion-item:first-of-type {
    border-radius: 0;
  }
  @media(max-width:1350px) {
    #Accordion-Container {
      flex: 1;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width:1000px) {
    #Accordion-Container {
      flex: 0.5;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width:800px) {
    .accordion-Section {
      flex-direction: column;
      height: 1000px;
      min-height: 0;
    }
    #Accordion-Container {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 500px;
    }
    .accordion-img {
      min-height: 498px;
    }
  }
</style>


<div class="accordion" id="Accordion-Container">
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
      <button
        class="accordion-button"
        type="button"
        data-bs-toggle="collapse"
        data-bs-target="#collapseOne"
        aria-expanded="true"
        aria-controls="collapseOne">
        Men's Shoes
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div
      id="collapseOne"
      class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
      aria-labelledby="headingOne"
      data-bs-parent="#Accordion-Container">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        They come in a variety of styles, including dress shoes, athletic shoes, boots, and sandals, and are made from a range of materials such as leather, suede, and canvas. Men's shoes are an important part of a man's wardrobe and can make a significant impact on his overall style and appearance.
        <a href="{{ section.settings.mensLink }}" class="accordion-btn button">Shop Now
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined arrow-btn">
            arrow_forward
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
      <button
        class="accordion-button collapsed"
        type="button"
        data-bs-toggle="collapse"
        data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="collapseTwo">
        Women's Shoes
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div
      id="collapseTwo"
      class="accordion-collapse collapse"
      aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
      data-bs-parent="#Accordion-Container">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        Not only functional but also serve as a fashion statement. They can elevate an outfit, add a pop of color, or complement a specific style. With a vast array of designs, colors, and materials, women's shoes provide endless possibilities for self-expression and personal style.
        <a href="{{ section.settings.womensLink }}" class="accordion-btn button">Shop Now
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined arrow-btn">
            arrow_forward
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
      <button
        class="accordion-button collapsed"
        type="button"
        data-bs-toggle="collapse"
        data-bs-target="#collapseThree"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="collapseThree">
        Kid's Shoes
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div
      id="collapseThree"
      class="accordion-collapse collapse"
      aria-labelledby="headingThree"
      data-bs-parent="#Accordion-Container">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        Kids shoes are created to ensure the well-being of children's feet as they grow. They offer comfort, support, and protection, all while being available in various sizes, colors, and styles. With a plethora of playful, colorful designs and more formal styles, kids shoes are not only practical but also a vital aspect of a child's fashion.
        <a href="{{ section.settings.kidsLink }}" class="accordion-btn button">Shop Now
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined arrow-btn">
            arrow_forward
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="accordion-img">
  <div class="img-container">
    <div class="image-class" id="imageOne"></div>
    <div class="image-class" id="imageTwo"></div>
    <div class="image-class" id="imageThree"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.9.1/gsap.min.js"></script>
<script>
  var accordionItems = document.querySelectorAll(".accordion-item");
  var imageContainers = document.querySelectorAll(".image-class");

  accordionItems.forEach(function(item, index) {
    var collapse = item.querySelector(".accordion-collapse");
    var image = imageContainers[index];

    collapse.addEventListener("shown.bs.collapse", function() {
      hideAllImages();
      image.style.display = "block";
      
      
    });
  });

  function hideAllImages() {
    imageContainers.forEach(function(image) {
      image.style.display = "none";
    });
  }
</script>


